passages.text:
The supernatural presence you felt when you entered the cave grows stronger, as if it is no longer dividing its attention between you and Thard but is focusing wholly on you. It seems to hover over you, as the unseen presence did in your dream, and you are certain that it is the same entity.

//"So you have taught others to defy me. No matter. It is you that I want!"//

<<include [[Cave noncombat possession]]>>

//A dark pathway, a cold breeze. The invisible presence that almost possessed your body looks down in disgust, then turns away. Your own inner rage is beginning to fade, along with all your other thoughts and emotions.

You shuffle forward, into the darkness. As your mind fades away, your last feeling is of triumph.//

[[THE END|Postscript]]

//A dark pathway, a cold breeze. The invisible presence that hovered over you gone, no longer interested in you. Your own inner rage is beginning to fade, along with all your other thoughts and emotions.

There is nothing left that can pull you back. You shuffle forward, into the darkness.//

[[THE END|Postscript]]

The supernatural presence grows stronger. It seems to hover over you, as the unseen presence did in your dream, and you are certain that it is the same entity.

//"Yes...you came, as I knew you would. You will be a fine vessel..."//

<<include [[Cave noncombat possession]]>>

//A dark pathway, a cold breeze.//

"My mind is a fortress. Its walls are stone, its gates are iron..."

//An invisible presence descending, clinging to you, using you as a conduit back into the world of the living.//

"Within the fortress is a garden. In it I keep all that is good and peaceful, all that I have built, all that makes me who I am..."

//Your inner rage, stirring in its dungeon, drawing strength from the presence. Never before has your rage seemed more like a foreign entity planted in your soul. It batters against the walls of your fortress, striving to tear them down more quickly than you can build them. //

<<if $discipline >= $EPIC_THRESHOLD>>\s
	//But your discipline is strong. Your fortress stands. Your rage is under your control, and the invading presence cannot use it to harm you. The presence batters against walls that it cannot penetrate. It draws away...//

	[[Let it go.|Cave possession resist let it go]]

	[[Harness your rage to destroy the invading presence.|Cave possession resist ritual dungeon]]
<<else>>\s
	//Your discipline is not strong enough. The fortress's walls crumble faster than you can restore them. The presence floods in, trampling the garden, heading for the conduit back into the living world.//

	[[You open your eyes.|Cave possessed and healed]]
<</if>>\s

//A dark pathway, a cold breeze. The invisible presence that hovered over you is within you now. It rages against the walls of the mental dungeon, but it cannot escape. It is already beginning to fade, along with your own inner rage, along with all your own thoughts and emotions.

There is nothing left that can pull you back. You shuffle forward, into the darkness. Your last thought is one of quiet triumph.//

[[THE END|Postscript]]

Config.saves.autosave = true;

Config.saves.isAllowed = function () {
	return !tags().includes("front-matter");
};

/* Background */
#background {
	background-color: #000000;	/* For browsers that don't support gradients */
	background: -webkit-linear-gradient(#000000 75%, #330000); /*Safari 5.1-6*/
	background: -o-linear-gradient(#000000 75%, #330000); /*Opera 11.1-12*/
	background: -moz-linear-gradient(#000000 75%, #330000); /*Fx 3.6-15*/
	background: linear-gradient(#000000 75%, #330000); /*Standard*/
	width: 100%;
	height: 100%;
	position: fixed;
	z-index: -10;
}


/* Game passages */
#passages {
	position: absolute;
	top: 0%;
	left: 50%;
	transform: translate(-50%, 0%);
	box-sizing: border-box;
	width: 40em;
	max-width: 100%;
	margin: 3em 0em 1em;	/* Top, sides, bottom */
	padding: 1.5em 2em 2em;	/* Top, sides, bottom */
	background-color: #FFFFFF;
	box-shadow: inset 0 0 1em #808000;
	color: #000000;
	border: 2px solid #404000;
	font-family: "Georgia", serif;
	font-size: 110%;
}

a {
	display: inline-block;
	color: #000000;
	background-color: #FFFFFF;
	border: 2px solid #CCCC99;
	border-radius: 12px;
	padding: 0px 6px;
}

a:hover {
	text-decoration: none;
	color: #000000;
	background-color: #CCCC99;
	border-color: #999966;
}


/* Stats box */
#stats-box {
	position: fixed;
	top: 4em;
	left: 2em;
	width: 10em;
	height: auto;
	font-family: sans-serif;
	font-variant: small-caps;
	color: #CCCCCC;
	font-size: 90%;
}

.statbar-back {
	position: relative;
	left: 0;
	top: 0;
	height: 1.5em;
	width: 10em;
	border-style: solid;
	border-width: 2px;
	border-radius: 1em;
	overflow: hidden;
	margin: 1em 0;
}

.statbar-text {
	position: absolute;
	left: 0.5em;
	top: 50%;
	width: 100%;
	transform: translate(0%, -50%);
}

.statbar-value {
	display: inline;
}

.statbar-fill {
	position: absolute;
	top: 0;
	left: 0;
	height: 100%;
	/* Width set by code */
}

.statbar-health {
	background: #116611;
}

.statbar-health-back {
	background: #001100;
	border-color: #333333;
}

.statbar-rage {
	background: #661111;
}

.statbar-rage-back {
	background: #110000;
	border-color: #333333;
}

.statbar-discipline {
	background: #111166;
}

.statbar-discipline-back {
	background: #000011;
	border-color: #333333;
}

.statbar-weapon-back {
	background: #101010;
	border-color: #333333;
}


/* Title screen and credits page */
.title-screen #passages {
	cursor: default;
}


.front-matter #passages {
	background-color: transparent;
	border: 0px;
	box-shadow: none;
	color: #FFFFFF;
	margin: 3em 0em 0em;	/* Top, sides, bottom */
}

.surtitle {
	display: inline-block;
	color: #FFFFFF;
	font-size: 125%;
	font-weight: bold;
	line-height: 1.25;
	letter-spacing: 0.25em;
	font-variant: small-caps;
}

.title {
	display: inline-block;
	padding: 0.25em 0.5em;
	border: 5px solid #660000;
	background-color: #CC0000;	/* For browsers that don't support gradients */
	background: -webkit-linear-gradient(100deg, #CC0000, #FFCCCC 60%, #CC0000); /*Safari 5.1-6*/
	background: -o-linear-gradient(100deg, #CC0000, #FFCCCC 60%, #CC0000); /*Opera 11.1-12*/
	background: -moz-linear-gradient(100deg, #CC0000, #FFCCCC 60%, #CC0000); /*Fx 3.6-15*/
	background: linear-gradient(100deg, #CC0000, #FFCCCC 60%, #CC0000); /*Standard*/
	color: #FFFFFF;
	font-size: 200%;
	font-weight: bold;
	line-height: 1.25;
	text-transform: uppercase;
}

.author {
	display: inline-block;
	margin-top: 0.75em;
	color: #FFFFFF;
	font-size: 100%;
	font-weight: bold;
}

.front-matter a {
	background: #331111;
	color: #FFFFFF;
	font-weight: bold;
	font-variant: small-caps;
	border: 2px solid #220000;
	border-radius: 0;
}

.front-matter a:hover {
	background-color: #CC3333;
	border: 2px solid #660000;
}

.disabled-button {
	display: inline-block;
	padding: 0px 6px;
	background: #111111;
	color: #CCCCCC;
	font-weight: bold;
	font-variant: small-caps;
	border: 2px solid #050505;
	border-radius: 0;
	cursor: default;
}


.inline-link a {
	display: inline;
	color: #FFFFFF;
	background-color: initial;
	border: initial;
	border-radius: initial;
	padding: initial;
	font-variant: none;
}

.inline-link a:hover {
	background-color: initial;
	border: initial;
	text-decoration: underline;
}

a.stats-box {
	display: inherit;
	color: inherit;
	background-color: inherit;
	border: inherit;
	border-radius: inherit;
	padding: inherit;
	font-variant: inherit;
	font-weight: inherit;
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0;
}

a.stats-box:hover {
	background-color: inherit;
	border: inherit;
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0;
}

/* Credits page social media icons */
.fa {
	padding: 0.55em 0.5em 0.45em;
	width: 1em;
	height: 1em;
	text-align: center;
	text-decoration: none;
	margin: 5px 2px;
	border-radius: 0;
    color: white;
	font-weight: normal !important;

}

.fa:hover {
	color: white;
	text-decoration: none;
	border: 2px solid #222222 !important;
}

.fa-facebook:hover {
    background: #3B5998 !important;
}

.fa-twitter:hover {
    background: #55ACEE !important;
}

.fa-wordpress:hover {
    background: #0087be !important;
}

.fa-patreon img {
	width: 13px;
	height: 13px;
}

.fa-patreon:hover {
    background: #F96854 !important;
}

.fa-home:hover {
    background: green !important;
}

.fa-envelope-o:hover {
	background: #666666 !important;
}

/* "Beome a patron" button */
a.become-a-patron {
	background: transparent;
	border: none;
	border-radius: 0;
	padding: 0px 0px;
}

a.become-a-patron:hover {
	background: transparent;
	border: none;
	border-radius: 0;
	padding: 0px 0px;
}

.become-a-patron img {
	height: 1.5em;
	width: auto;

}


/* Small screen/mobile formatting */
@media screen and (max-width: 68em) {
	#passages {
		font-size: 100%;
		padding: 1em 1em 2em;	/* Top, sides, bottom */
		margin: 3em 0em 0em;	/* Top, sides, bottom */
	}

	#stats-box {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0%;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translate(-50%, 0%);
		box-sizing: border-box;
		width: 45em;	/* Width plus padding of passage area, plus 1em to make sure it hides passage's border */
		max-width: 100%;
		height: 3em;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 0.5em 0em;
		margin: 0;
			/* Fade from black to transparent */
		background-color: #000000;	/* For browsers that don't support gradients */
		background: -webkit-linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,1) 66%,rgba(0,0,0,0)); /*Safari 5.1-6*/
		background: -o-linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,1) 66%,rgba(0,0,0,0)); /*Opera 11.1-12*/
		background: -moz-linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,1) 66%,rgba(0,0,0,0)); /*Fx 3.6-15*/
		background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,1) 66%, rgba(0,0,0,0)); /*Standard*/
	}

	.statbar-back {
		display: inline-block;
		width: 23%;
		height: 2em;
		margin: 0 0;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	.statbar-text {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 75%;
		left: 0;
	}

	.statbar-value {
		display: block;
	}
}


/* Debug box (will not appear correctly on mobile) */
#debug-box {
	font-family: monospace;
	color: #333333;
	font-size: 75%;
	position: fixed;
	right: 10px;
	bottom: 10px;
}

#debug-box a {
	background: transparent;
	color: #333333;
	border-color: #333333;
}

input[type="text"] {
	color: #000000;
}

/* Inline debug messages */
.debug {
	font-family: monospace;
	background-color: #CCCCCC;
}
